704269f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Linden Boulevard
704269f-a.text:
(1)
Flatbush Ave., east side, between Linden Boulevard and Martense
Street. In background, are rears of frame homes facing on East 21st
Street; between them is the top of the Union League Club.
January 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, from a slightly different angle.
January 1929.
Eugene L. Arnbruster Collection.
